graphs-data.question: I was satisfied with the final design/output
graphs-data.column_insight_ultra_summary: The survey data analysis shows high customer satisfaction with the services provided, particularly in 'Advertisement/Twitter Card', 'Flyer/Sales Sheet/Fact Sheet', and 'Graph/Table/Organizational and Flow Chart' projects. However, 'Proposal/Bid' and 'Placemat' projects, as well as streamlining the submission process, improving quality consistency, and enhancing communication, require attention. Despite high satisfaction across all firms, variations in scores suggest opportunities for specific firms to improve.
